    <detaileddescription>
<para>classification of the triangles around one vertex, packed in 32 bits; it stores 1-bit flag (hasRepeatedVerts) and either 31-bit numRepeatedVerts (if the flag is on), or 16-bit numOpenChains and 15-bit numClosedChains (if the flag is off) </para>
